<subSubSection id="AA91656F4B62FFCFFF09F8020746F82D" pageId="7" pageNumber="556" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="E23436E44B62FFCFFF09F8020746F82D" blockId="7.[151,1436,1964,2024]" pageId="7" pageNumber="556">
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B62FFCFFF09F8020339F800" bold="true" box="[151,266,1964,1989]" pageId="7" pageNumber="556">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. First flagellomere pointed at tip. Basal segment of arista 
<number id="544324C34B62FFCFFC34F80201FEF801" box="[938,973,1964,1988]" pageId="7" pageNumber="556" value="0.1">0.1</number>
times as long as apical portion of arista (
<figureCitation id="7AB02A614B62FFCFFF01F86102C0F82D" box="[159,243,1999,2024]" captionStart="FIGURES 16 – 17" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1343,1365]" captionTargetBox="[284,1268,205,1303]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[226,1360,175,1339]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 16 – 17. Hercostomus flavus sp. nov., male. 16. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 17. Genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: epn = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, lat = epandrial lobe, pos = postgonite, cer = cercus." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/226275/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="556">
Fig. 
<number id="544324C34B62FFCFFF4AF86102C0F82D" box="[212,243,1999,2024]" pageId="7" pageNumber="556" value="16.0">16</number>
</figureCitation>
). Cercus mainly brown, but yellowish at base, nearly triangular, with several long digitations (
<figureCitation id="7AB02A614B62FFCFFA8AF8610754F82D" box="[1300,1383,1999,2024]" captionStart="FIGURES 16 – 17" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1343,1365]" captionTargetBox="[284,1268,205,1303]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[226,1360,175,1339]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 16 – 17. Hercostomus flavus sp. nov., male. 16. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 17. Genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: epn = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, lat = epandrial lobe, pos = postgonite, cer = cercus." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/226275/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="556">
Fig. 
<number id="544324C34B62FFCFFAD6F87E0754F82D" box="[1352,1383,2000,2024]" pageId="7" pageNumber="556" value="17.0">17</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
