<subSubSection id="AA91656F4B6DFFC1FF59FA34077CFF3D" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="558" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" type="description">
<paragraph id="E23436E44B6DFFC1FF59FA34077CFF3D" blockId="8.[151,1437,1434,2038]" lastBlockId="9.[151,1437,151,464]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="558" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B6DFFC0FF59FA340362FA76" bold="true" box="[199,337,1434,1459]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Description</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B6DFFC0FEFFFA3403ADFA76" bold="true" box="[353,414,1434,1459]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Male</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation id="7AB02A614B6DFFC0FE31FA3403C5FA76" box="[431,502,1434,1459]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1553,1575]" captionText="FIGURE 4. Hercostomus flavus sp. nov. Male. Scale bar = 1.0 mm." pageId="8" pageNumber="557">
Fig. 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FE7BFA3503C5FA76" box="[485,502,1435,1459]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
). Body length 
<quantity id="25739B014B6DFFC0FD3EFA3500C9FA77" box="[672,762,1435,1459]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.4" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" unit="mm" value="3.4">3.4 mm</quantity>
, wing length 
<quantity id="25739B014B6DFFC0FC09FA3401C1FA77" box="[919,1010,1434,1459]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" unit="mm" value="3.5">3.5 mm</quantity>
. 
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B6DFFC0FC60FA34060DFA76" bold="true" box="[1022,1086,1434,1459]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Head</emphasis>
dark metallic green, with pale gray pollinosity; face gradually narrowed downward. Hairs and bristles on head black, postocular bristles black, posteroventral hairs pale. Antenna black (
<figureCitation id="7AB02A614B6DFFC0FDE5FA4C00E3FA3E" box="[635,720,1506,1531]" captionStart="FIGURES 16 – 17" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1343,1365]" captionTargetBox="[284,1268,205,1303]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[226,1360,175,1339]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 16 – 17. Hercostomus flavus sp. nov., male. 16. Antenna, scale bar = 0.2 mm; 17. Genitalia, lateral view, scale bar = 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: epn = epandrium, hyp = hypandrium, ph = phallus, sur = surstylus, lat = epandrial lobe, pos = postgonite, cer = cercus." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/226275/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">
Fig. 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD2CFA4C00E3FA3E" box="[690,720,1506,1531]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="16.0">16</number>
</figureCitation>
), first flagellomere slightly brownish at tip; first flagellomere pointed at tip, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FEDFF9A90357F9DA" box="[321,356,1543,1567]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.3">1.3</number>
times longer than wide, with brown pubescence; arista subapical, longer than width of head, black, almost bare, basal segment 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD83F9850073F986" box="[541,576,1579,1603]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="0.1">0.1</number>
times as long as apical portion of arista. Proboscis dark yellow with brown hairs; palpus dark brown, with pale hairs and 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD01F9E1009EF9A2" box="[671,685,1615,1639]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="3.0">3</number>
black dorsal bristles at tip. 
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B6DFFC0FC77F9E00671F9A2" bold="true" box="[1001,1090,1614,1639]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Thorax</emphasis>
dark metallic green, with pale gray pollinosity. Hairs and bristles on thorax black; 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD47F9DC00D4F94E" box="[729,743,1650,1675]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="6.0">6</number>
long, strong dc, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FC3DF9DD01FEF94E" box="[931,973,1651,1675]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="8.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="8.0">8–9</number>
pairs of acr. Scutellum with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FA90F9DD072FF94E" box="[1294,1308,1651,1675]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
pairs of sc, inner pair long strong, outer pair very short. 
<emphasis id="D0FFEAF64B6DFFC0FD11F93800F4F96A" bold="true" box="[655,711,1686,1711]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Legs</emphasis>
mainly black, fore leg mainly blackish, but trochanters and mid portions of tibiae yellow; fore and mid tarsi brown to black toward tip. Hairs and bristles on legs black. Fore coxa with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FF51F97102EEF932" box="[207,221,1759,1783]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
d at apical half; with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FE51F97103EEF932" box="[463,477,1759,1783]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
apical bristles. Mid coxa with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FCA8F9710177F932" box="[822,836,1759,1783]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
d at middle. 
<collectingCountry id="9A9C76744B6DFFC0FC4BF970063EF932" box="[981,1037,1758,1783]" name="India" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Hind</collectingCountry>
coxa with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FB16F97106A5F932" box="[1160,1174,1759,1783]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
outer bristle. Fore tibia with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FF4EF8AD02EDF8DE" box="[208,222,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
weak ad, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FECFF8AD036CF8DE" box="[337,351,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
pd, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FE0FF8AD03ACF8DE" box="[401,415,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
av; with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD94F8AD002BF8DE" box="[522,536,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
apical bristles. Mid tibia with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FCEDF8AD01B2F8DE" box="[883,897,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="3.0">3</number>
ad, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FC2FF8AD018CF8DE" box="[945,959,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
pd, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FC6FF8AD01CCF8DE" box="[1009,1023,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
pv; with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FBF2F8AD0649F8DE" box="[1132,1146,1795,1819]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="3.0">3</number>
apical bristles. 
<collectingCountry id="9A9C76744B6DFFC0FAB5F8AC0750F8DE" box="[1323,1379,1794,1819]" name="India" pageId="8" pageNumber="557">Hind</collectingCountry>
tibia with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FF4EF88802EDF8FA" box="[208,222,1830,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="5.0">5</number>
short ad in 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FEFCF8890343F8FA" box="[354,368,1831,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
row, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FE30F889038FF8FA" box="[430,444,1831,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
d, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FE41F88903DEF8FA" box="[479,493,1831,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
pd, 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD80F889001FF8FA" box="[542,556,1831,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="1.0">1</number>
av; with 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FD08F8890097F8FA" box="[662,676,1831,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.0">2</number>
apical bristles. Relative length of tibia and 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FB15F88806AAF8FA" box="[1163,1177,1830,1855]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="5.0">5</number>
tarsomeres of legs LI: 
<number id="544324C34B6DFFC0FF09F8E40289F8A6" box="[151,186,1866,1891]" pageId="8" pageNumber="557" value="2.6">2.6</number>
: 
